"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"What do the following have in common?\\n\\n* Agile Software Development\\n* Six Sigma\\n* Behavior Driven Development\\n* Software Craftsmanship\\n* DevOps\\n\\nEach of these represents a good idea that a group of well-meaning people tried (and succeeded) to spread into the world.\\n\\nEach is generally poorly defined and poorly understood.\\n\\nEach term has now lost its meaning.\\n\\nEach term, with new watered-down, wrong-headed interpretations is being used constantly to create a false sense of security and justification for bad practices.\\n\\nIn each case, adoption of a good idea is being accidentally replaced by adoption of a name which represents that good idea. The term becomes a placeholder for good intention.\\n\\nI can “do BDD” in the same way that I can sign up for a membership at a gym. I feel the sense of accomplishment without the need to actually get healthy.\",\"timestamp\":1638818003,\"title\":\"The Curse of a Name: How to Kill a Good Idea\"},\"digest\":\"YXit9kaf5QKxiO_HrxP0A65c82GpcYZPMBdygIDjcz4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x46a8E86e3195315E438C7d38176992e9CF46a5Dc\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"I7P4afKDa_JKmjo9D0PMbGmYZpczZYHz3SYtacEjrtk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"UikzSvTrLuoVELXoMLx1An58t74a7XRzhtGv_q42aTM\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"3CsRRdCI4aOq9VAoBvu80S5pJOMii_n6SNRMvL7VSlelDtkGPFYdtCjy1H_GcEo61_5q3D7FELCOfTYJkJr1qQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x09d8772328ce085cb7fd9b72f93ca63112290d42c734029af857c5a4568b093a3fc792ad72533ac47d8a43ab8fb7bd4bf43dc5a1a1c649cf805ed7cd187c4df61c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"I7P4afKDa_JKmjo9D0PMbGmYZpczZYHz3SYtacEjrtk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"UikzSvTrLuoVELXoMLx1An58t74a7XRzhtGv_q42aTM\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"